'''斯洛伐克廣播電視'''（{{lang-sk|Rozhlas a televízia Slovenska}}），簡稱'''RTVS'''，是[[斯洛伐克|斯洛伐克]]的國有[[公共廣播|公共廣播]]，總部位於[[布拉提斯拉瓦|布拉提斯拉瓦]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Organizačná štruktúra {{!}} Rozhlas a televízia Slovenska|url=http://www.rtvs.org/o-rtvs/organizacna-struktura|publisher=Rozhlas a televízia Slovenska|accessdate=12 March 2014|language=sk|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314224019/https://www.rtvs.org/o-rtvs/organizacna-struktura|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=EBU-UER / New chief executive appointed to Radio and Television Slovakia (RTVS)|url=http://www3.ebu.ch/cms/sites/ebu/contents/news/2012/08/new-chief-executive-appointed-to.html|publisher=European Broadcasting Union|accessdate=12 March 2014|date=15 August 2012|archive-date=2018-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831174755/https://www.ebu.ch/cms/sites/ebu/contents/news/2012/08/new-chief-executive-appointed-to.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該組織創建於2011年，由[[斯洛伐克電視台|斯洛伐克電視台]]和斯洛伐克廣播電台合併而成<ref name=Merger>{{cite news|last=Balogová|first=Beata|title=RTVS arrives; Nižňanský leaves|url=http://spectator.sme.sk/articles/view/41254/2/rtvs_arrives_niznansky_leave.html|accessdate=12 March 2014|newspaper=The Slovak Spectator|date=10 January 2011|archive-date=2014-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312213552/http://spectator.sme.sk/articles/view/41254/2/rtvs_arrives_niznansky_leave.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。斯洛伐克廣播電視是[[歐洲廣播聯盟|歐洲廣播聯盟]]成員。
